display_name: Diastolic blood pressure (DBP) (mean of 6 measurements)
description: Blood pressure (BP) is collected six times, three measurements in the evening and three in the morning. This is the mean of the diastolic measurements at each time point.

display_name: Heart Rate (mean of 6 measurements)
description: Blood pressure (BP) is collected six times, three measurements in the evening and three in the morning. This is the mean of the heart rate measurements at each time point.

display_name: Systolic blood pressure (SBP) (mean of 6 measurements)

display_name: Number of missing diastolic measurements

display_name: Number of missing systolic measurements

display_name: Overall arousal index
description: Total number of arousals per hour of sleep. Ratio of count of arousals to total sleep time in hours. [(Total number of arousals) / (hours of sleep)]
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;rem;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;rapid eye movement

display_name: Average oxygen saturation (SaO2) in sleep time
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;rem;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;rapid eye movement;%
calculation: ( ( avsao2nh ) * ( timest1p + timest2p + times34p ) + ( avsao2rh ) * ( timeremp ) ) / 100

display_name: Minimum oxygen saturation (SaO2) in sleep time
description: Lowest oxygen saturation (SaO2)% during sleep
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;rem;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;rapid eye movement;%

display_name: Obstructive apnea (all oxygen desaturations) hypopnea (>= 3% oxygen desaturation) index
description: Ratio of the count of all obstructive apneas (all desaturations) plus the count of hypopneas associated with at least a >=3% oxygen desaturation to the total sleep time expressed in hours.
calculation: 60*(hrembp3 + hrop3 + hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop ) / slpprdp

display_name: Obstructive Apnea Index all oxygen desaturations
description: Obstructive Apnea Index at all desaturations  [(Total number of obstructive apneas associated with all desaturations) / (hours of sleep)]

display_name: Percent of sleep time <70% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 70% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Percent of sleep time <75% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 75% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Percent of sleep time <80% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 80% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Percent of sleep time <85% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 85% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Percent of sleep time <90% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 90% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Percent of sleep time <95% oxygen saturation (SaO2)
description: Ratio of the number of minutes with oxygen saturation (SaO2) under 95% to the total sleep time expressed in hours.

display_name: Overall Respiratory Disturbance Index (RDI) at >=3% oxygen desaturation
description: [(total number of apneas and hypopneas associated with >= 3% oxygen desaturation) / (hours of sleep)]
labels: psg;non-rem; non rem;%;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;nrem;rem;rapid eye movement
calculation: 60 * ( hrembp3 + hrop3 + hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + carbp3 + carop3 + canbp3 + canop3 + oarbp3 + oarop3 + oanbp3 + oanop3 ) / slpprdp

display_name: Sleep efficiency
description: Percentage of time in bed that was spent sleeping, or the ratio of total sleep time to total time in bed, expressed as a percentage.   [100*(total sleep time) / (total time in bed)]
labels: psg;non-rem; non rem;%;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;nrem;rem;rapid eye movement

display_name: Total sleep time
description: Total time from lights out to lights on that is scored as sleep (rounded to nearest minute)
labels: non-rem; non rem;non-rapid eye movement;non rapid;nrem;psg;rem;rapid eye movement

display_name: Time in rapid eye movement sleep (REM)
description: Total time scored as rapid eye movement sleep (REM) rounded to nearest minute

display_name: Percent of sleep time in rapid eye movement sleep (REM)
description: [100*(number of minutes scored as REM) / (total sleep time)] * 100

display_name: Percent of sleep time in Stage 3-4
description: [100*(number of minutes scored as stage 3-4 sleep)/(total sleep time)]

display_name: Time in Stage 1 sleep
description: Total time scored as stage 1 sleep rounded to nearest minute
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;non-rapid eye movement sleep;non rapid

display_name: Percent of sleep time in Stage 1 sleep
description: [100*(number of minutes scored as stage 1 sleep)/(total sleep time)]
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;non-rapid eye movement sleep;non rapid;%

display_name: Time in Stage 2 sleep
description: Total time scored as stage 2 sleep rounded to nearest minute
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;non-rapid eye movement sleep;non rapid

display_name: Percent of sleep time in Stage 2 sleep
description: [100*(number of minutes scored as stage 2 sleep)/(total sleep time)]
labels: psg;non-rem;non rem;nrem;non-rapid eye movement sleep;non rapid;%

display_name: Time in Stage 3/4 sleep
description: Total time scored as stage 3/4 sleep rounded to nearest minute

display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 3% - number of [all apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 3% oxygen desaturation] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hrembp3 + hrop3 + hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 3% - number of [all apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 3% oxygen desaturation or arousal] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hremba3 + hroa3 + hnrba3 + hnroa3 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 4% - number of [all apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 4% oxygen desaturation] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hrembp4 + hrop4 + hnrbp4 + hnrop4 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 4% - number of [all apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 4% oxygen desaturation or arousal] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hremba4 + hroa4 + hnrba4 + hnroa4 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

display_name: Central Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 3% - number of [central apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 3% oxygen desaturation] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hrembp3 + hrop3 + hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop) / slpprdp

display_name: Central Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 3% - number of [central apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 3% oxygen desaturation or arousal] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hremba3 + hroa3 + hnrba3 + hnroa3 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop) / slpprdp

display_name: Central Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 4% - number of [central apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 4% oxygen desaturation] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hrembp4 + hrop4 + hnrbp4 + hnrop4 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop) / slpprdp

display_name: Central Apnea-Hypopnea Index (AHI) >= 4% - number of [central apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 4% oxygen desaturation or arousal] per hour of sleep
calculation: 60 * (hremba4 + hroa4 + hnrba4 + hnroa4 + carbp + carop + canbp + canop) / slpprdp

display_name: Obstructive Apnea-Hypopnea Index (OAHI) >= 3% - number of [obstructive apneas] and [hypopneas with >= 3% oxygen desaturation] per hour of sleep

calculation: 60 * (hremba3 + hroa3 + hnrba3 + hnroa3 + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

calculation: 60 * (hrembp4 + hrop4 + hnrbp4 + hnrop4 + oarbp + oarop + oanbp + oanop) / slpprdp

Self-reported daily nap time in minutes (all days)
description: Calculated as a weighted average of self-reported daily nap time from weekdays and from weekends (ynaptime_s = 5/7 * ywd_napdur  + 2/7*ywe_napdur)

display_name: Self-reported sleep latency
description: Calculated from self report of hours and minutes it takes to fall asleep (ysleeplatency = (yflashr * 60) + yflasmn)

display_name: Self-reported sleep time across all days
description: Calculated as a weighted average of self-reported sleep time from weekdays and from weekends (ysleeptime_hr  = 5/7 *wd_slpdur_hr  + 2/7*we_slpdur_hr)

display_name: Sleep time from self-reported bed and wake times in minutes (all days)
description: Calculated as a weighted average of self-reported sleep time from weekdays and from weekends (ysleeptime_min = 5/7 * wd_slpdur  + 2/7*we_slpdur )

display_name: Sleep time from self-reported usual sleep time (all days)
description: Calculated as a weighted average of self-reported usual sleep time from weekdays and from weekends (ysleeptime_s = 5/7 * ywd_slpdur  + 2/7*ywe_slpdur )

display_name: Rate socioeconomic standing based on ladder

display_name: Self-reported daily nap time in minutes (Weekend)

display_name: Sleep time from self-reported usual sleep time (Weekend)
